Huatai’s Xu ‘Bullish’ on ICBC’s Earnings This Quarter and Next

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-30T08:25:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/huatai-s-xu-bullish-on-icbc-s-earnings-this-quarter-and-next.html
Xu Guoyu, an analyst at Huatai
Securities Co., comments on the outlook for  Industrial &
Commercial Bank of China (601398)  Ltd., the nation’s biggest lender,
after its shares climbed today. Xu spoke by phone from Nanjing.  “ICBC is a solid bank that may be on the rebound path. We
are bullish on its second- and third-quarter performance.  ‘‘ICBC has enough of a deposit cushion to help it meet
regulators’ loan-to-deposit requirements.’’  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chitra Somayaji at 
 csomayaji@bloomberg.net  